VALUES
('Venus', 2, 1, 'Welcome to Venus Haven, a luxurious retreat inspired by the enchanting beauty of the planet Venus. Step into one of our Venus themed rooms and immerse yourself in a celestial paradise. The moment you enter, you will be captivated by the ethereal ambiance, featuring warm hues of soft pinks and oranges that emulate the breathtaking Venusian sunset. The Venus Suite boasts a spacious and elegantly designed bedroom, adorned with plush furnishings and tasteful decor. Sink into the lavish queen-size bed, adorned with silky-smooth sheets and plush pillows, ensuring a restful and rejuvenating sleep. Let the gentle glow of Venus fill the room through carefully placed ambient lighting, creating an atmosphere of tranquility and romance. Indulge in panoramic views of the Venusian landscape through the floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing you to witness the celestial beauty and ever-changing colors of the planet. Relax in the cozy seating area, featuring plush armchairs and a charming Venus-inspired coffee table, perfect for savoring a cup of celestial-inspired tea or indulging in a captivating book.', 209000.00, 'https://example.com/room1.jpg', true),
('Moon', 3, 2, 'Welcome to Lunar Retreat, where celestial dreams come true. Step into our Moonlight Suite and immerse yourself in a captivating lunar experience. As you enter, you will be greeted by a serene ambiance with soft, moonlit hues and celestial decor that evokes the tranquil beauty of the moon. The room features a comfortable king-size bed with luxurious, cloud-like bedding that will transport you to a peaceful slumber under the moons gentle glow.  Indulge in the breathtaking views of the moons surface through the large panoramic window, allowing you to gaze upon the mystique and wonder of the lunar landscape. Relax in the cozy seating area, designed to resemble a lunar rover, where you can unwind and plan your lunar adventures.', 325000.00, 'https://example.com/room2.jpg', true),
('Jupiter', 3, 3, 'Welcome to Jupiter Oasis, an extraordinary retreat that embodies the grandeur and majesty of the largest planet in our solar system. Step into one of our Jupiter Suites and embark on a celestial journey like no other. As you enter, you will be greeted by an ambiance that evokes the awe-inspiring beauty of the gas giant. The Jupiter Suites offer spacious and opulent bedrooms, adorned with luxurious furnishings and celestial-themed decor. Immerse yourself in the plush comfort of the king-size bed, adorned with exquisite linens and adorned pillows, ensuring a blissful nights sleep. Gaze up at the ceiling, where a mesmerizing mural depicts the swirling storms and colorful bands that define Jupiters atmosphere. Experience panoramic views of the surrounding cosmos through the expansive windows that showcase the breathtaking beauty of the outer space. Marvel at the mesmerizing dance of Jupiters moons and the swirling storms that grace its surface. Unwind in the cozy seating area, complete with plush armchairs and a Jupiter-inspired coffee table, where you can enjoy a cup of celestial-themed coffee or engage in captivating conversations.', 400000.00, 'https://example.com/room3.jpg', true);
